ed favour from God, and God possess tremendous favour, His appointed Imam is he who guide to the right path, verily the legacy of God has come to you, O the family of Yaseen.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "SALAAMUN A’LAA AALE YAASIN ZAALE-KA WA HOWAL FAZ-LUL MOBEENA MIN I’NDAL LAAHO WALLAAHO ZUL-FAZLIL A’ZEEME IMAAME-HI SERAATE-HIL MUSTA-QEEME QAD AATAA KOMUL-LAAHO KHELAA-FATE-HI YAA AALE YAASIN.", "ArabicText1": "سَلَامٌ عَلٰى آلِ يٰس ذٰلِكَ وَهُوَ الْفَضْلُ الْمُبِیْنَ مِنْ عِنْدَ اللهُ وَاللهُ ذُوالْفَضْلِ الْعَظِیْمِ اِمَامِهٖ صِرَاطِهِ الْمُسْتَقِیْمِ قَدْ آتَا كُمُ اللهُ خِلَافَتِهٖ یَا آلِ یٰس۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "